name: query
msg
VR_EM
data process
func:
let array = []

for (var i = 0; i < msg.payload.length; i++)
{
    var topic = msg.payload[i]
    var old_name = msg.payload[i].b +'.' + msg.payload[i].d +'.' + msg.payload[i].old_limit
    var old_value = global.get(old_name)

    var new_tag = msg.payload[i].f
    var new_value = global.get(new_tag)

    var obj  = {
                old_tag:old_name,
                old_value:old_value,
                new_tag:new_tag,
                new_value:new_value,
                register:msg.payload[i].write_reg_id,
                qnty:msg.payload[i].addr_qty,
                fc:msg.payload[i].fun_code,
                unit_id:msg.payload[i].unit_id,
                reg_type:msg.payload[i].write_reg_type,
                p:msg.payload[i].p,
                b:msg.payload[i].b,
                d:msg.payload[i].d
                }
    obj.topic = topic
    array.push(obj)
}
msg.payload = array
return msg;
